{
  "texts": [
    "It tells us which image tokens have the most influence on which latent feature.",
    "The mean along the latent sequence thus gives us the most important image regions according to the vision resampler.",
    "How can we use this information to determine which of these regions corresponds to which word?",
    "One idea is to give higher weights to the latents that correspond to the words we are interested in.",
    "We get these weights by looking at the cross-attention scores of the last XATTN layer."
  ]
}